1.0.name: wordpress/fixed-menu
1.0.description:
Fixed Menu is plugin to place the assembled menu in theme, sidebar widget and content (shortcode).

Translators

  • Japanese (ja) - AI.Takeuchi

If you have created your own language pack, or have an update of an existing one, you can send gettext PO and MO files to me so that I can bundle it into Fixed Menu. You can download the latest POT file from here.
